Detailed Description

Dialog based represenation of any UI-Component.

This component provides also a menu command and can be integrated into a consumer of ibase::ICommandsProvider interface.

virtual const ibase::IHierarchicalCommand* iqtgui::CDialogGuiComp::GetCommands ( ) const [virtual]

Get list of menu commands.

These commands will be integrated in global menu system, independent from actual selected view. For support of normal pull down menu, depth of this tree structure should be at least 3.
